"title": "6142: decay",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6142: decay",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>As a consequence of the fall, all created things have a tendency to waste away and spoil. Jesus Christ brings deliverance from this.</p>\n<h2>Decay was decreed as a result of the fall</h2>\n<h3>In human beings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:17\">GEN 2:17</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:17–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:20\">ROM 8:20</a></p>\n<h2>Decay is the common experience of humanity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:3-Ps90:10\">PSA 90:3–90:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:8-Ps49:9\">PSA 49:8–49:9</a></p>\n<h2>A decaying world is not worth clinging to</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19-Matt6:20\">MAT 6:19–6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:26\">PSA 102:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33\">LUK 12:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15-1John2:17\">1JN 2:15–2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is free from decay</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:24-Acts2:31\">ACT 2:24–2:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:8-Ps16:11\">PSA 16:8–16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:34-Acts13:37\">ACT 13:34–13:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26\">HEB 7:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:8\">HEB 13:8</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are redeemed from decay</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:16\">2CO 4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:26\">JOB 19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a></p>\n<h2>Christians are ``salt'' in a decaying world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:13\">MAT 5:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:50\">MRK 9:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:34\">LUK 14:34</a></p>\n<h2>The world to come is free from decay</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:21\">ROM 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42\">1CO 15:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28\">HEB 12:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:14\">HEB 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of the link between sin and decay</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:14-Lev26:16\">LEV 26:14–26:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:39\">LEV 26:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:20-Num5:22\">NUM 5:20–5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:27\">NUM 5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:22\">DEU 28:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:24\">DEU 32:24</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:13\">JOB 18:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3\">PSA 32:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:13-Ps49:14\">PSA 49:13–49:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:15\">PSA 106:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:43\">PSA 106:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:10\">PSA 112:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:24\">ISA 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:16\">ISA 10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:4\">ISA 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:16\">ISA 24:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:7\">ISA 64:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:7\">JER 49:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:6\">LAM 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:8\">LAM 2:8</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:17\">EZK 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:23\">EZK 24:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:10\">EZK 33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:3\">HOS 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:10\">HOS 8:10</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:16\">HAB 3:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:2\">JAS 5:2</a></p>",
